## dp_leaking_1s_very_d@angerous

看题目就知道是个 dp(dq) 泄露问题
之前[详细推导](https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_52446095/article/details/115445313?ops_request_misc=%257B%2522request%255Fid%2522%253A%2522162089763116780262561085%2522%252C%2522scm%2522%253A%252220140713.130102334.pc%255Fblog.%2522%257D&request_id=162089763116780262561085&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~blog~first_rank_v2~rank_v29-2-115445313.pc_v2_rank_blog_default&utm_term=dp)过，这里不再赘述
直接抄代码：

```python
from Crypto.Util.number import *

e = 65537
n = 
c = 
dp = 734763139918837027274765680404546851353356952885439663987181004382601658386317353877499122276686150509151221546249750373865024485652349719427182780275825

for k in range(1, e):
    p = (e*dp-1) // k +1
    q = n // p
    if (n - p*q) == 0:
        break
print(p, q)
phi = (p-1) * (q-1)
d = inverse(e, phi)
print(d)
m = pow(c, d, n)
print(long_to_bytes(m))
```
结果为：wctf2020{dp_leaking_1s_very_d@angerous}
